39:16.564 --> 39:20.109
Alright, fine, just, uh... leave it here
for right now, but don't go anywhere

39:21.026 --> 39:22.194
- OK?
- OK.

39:31.996 --> 39:33.873
- Yeah?
<i>- Julia's skip is missing</i>

39:33.998 --> 39:36.458
<i>from her storage locker
so Sammy and I are gonna go.</i>

39:37.084 --> 39:39.879
We're gonna go check on
her neighbour, Wendy.

39:40.045 --> 39:41.088
<i>What are you up to?</i>

39:41.171 --> 39:43.173
Uh, we've been looking
for that English woman.

39:43.299 --> 39:45.134
- Yeah?
<i>- Yeah, Carly's been helping.</i>

39:45.301 --> 39:46.927
She's on a scout, as we speak.

39:47.887 --> 39:49.263
You got Carly working this?

39:49.430 --> 39:50.723
Otto, she's doing a scout

39:51.056 --> 39:53.475
and how old was I
when you started putting me to work?

39:53.559 --> 39:54.643
<i>No, no, no.</i>

39:54.894 --> 39:57.146
That was different. You're you.

39:57.730 --> 39:59.148
And Carly's not a kid anymore.

39:59.690 --> 40:01.358
<i>I know, I... I just worry.</i>

40:01.609 --> 40:07.114
Look, I... I know this woman's a Brit,
but she's also a con artist, right?

40:07.740 --> 40:08.782
It's dangerous.

40:09.408 --> 40:11.493
I just wanted you to have backup.

40:12.036 --> 40:13.162
Otto, what have you done?

40:13.913 --> 40:15.915
Reach under the driver's seat.

40:23.964 --> 40:24.924
What?

40:25.507 --> 40:29.261
Only in this family could something
like this count as a romantic gesture.

40:40.814 --> 40:41.899
Can I help you?

40:42.483 --> 40:43.359
Um...

40:43.984 --> 40:45.986
Do you, uh, have any Hardy Boys?

40:46.362 --> 40:48.238
My dad... he collects them.

40:48.405 --> 40:51.033
I love the Hardy Boys.
If we do, they're over there.

40:51.492 --> 40:52.368
Thanks.

41:00.751 --> 41:04.672
Hey, Dad.
Yeah, I'm at this... I'm at the flea market

41:04.797 --> 41:08.133
and, um, I'm looking for those, uh...

41:08.300 --> 41:12.012
blue spines, and I'm just, um,
not seeing them.

41:13.055 --> 41:14.098
Yeah, no, I'll, um...

41:14.139 --> 41:17.434
just do a little more digging.

41:20.312 --> 41:21.188
Bye.

41:23.148 --> 41:24.024
Thank you.

41:36.453 --> 41:38.414
Oh! Goddamn it!

41:38.497 --> 41:41.166
Get the... give me my chips.
Give me my chips.

41:41.500 --> 41:43.377
All my life savings right there.

41:43.585 --> 41:46.505
Kid, you better give me my chips,
before I take this wheelchair

41:46.588 --> 41:49.216
and wrap it around your ass!
Come on, give me my chips!

42:23.125 --> 42:24.043
Shit.

42:24.334 --> 42:26.587
Hey, buddy, you got a leak.

42:32.968 --> 42:34.261
Aw, fuck me.

42:41.518 --> 42:42.394
Ahem.

42:42.895 --> 42:44.229
Check it out, Cheetos are back.

42:45.022 --> 42:46.774
You want one? It's on me.

42:47.483 --> 42:49.485
- We need to talk.
- OK.

42:49.902 --> 42:50.778
What's up?

42:51.987 --> 42:54.531
The results came back on the blood
we found from Winslow's car.

42:54.573 --> 42:57.284
Belongs to a post-menopausal
Caucasian woman.

42:59.578 --> 43:00.454
OK.

43:02.039 --> 43:04.583
I'm gonna need a cheek swab
from your grandmother to test for DNA.

43:05.084 --> 43:07.252
- Oh, my God...
- I want her to do it voluntarily

43:07.294 --> 43:09.671
but if she refuses,
I'll compel her with a court order.

43:10.589 --> 43:12.466
- OK.
- Just wanted to give you a heads up.

43:37.616 --> 43:40.702
- How'd you know I'd come out the back?
- Skip tracer 101.

43:41.703 --> 43:43.914
- So the girl's out front?
- Granddaughter.

43:44.623 --> 43:45.791
It's family business.

43:47.876 --> 43:49.336
What if I had a gun, Audrey?

43:50.170 --> 43:52.422
I saw the pictures she took
of that stupid purse.

43:53.382 --> 43:55.634
Unless you have a derringer,
I wasn't worried.

43:57.136 --> 43:59.054
My bag, however...

44:07.187 --> 44:09.273
Are you sure this
is the right Wendy?

44:09.773 --> 44:12.109
That's what my guy
over at Records says.

44:12.234 --> 44:13.318
Oh, dearie me...

44:15.904 --> 44:17.281
Otto!

44:17.406 --> 44:18.365
Jesus!
